t, please."],[379,433,"Please. - It's okay."],[538,625,"No, please!"],[629,667,"Come on,"],[667,738,"sweetheart. - Mrs. Grant, please!"],[738,809,"I've waited long enough."],[809,971,"No, stop, let go of me!"],[1021,1142,"Please, Mrs. Grant!"],[1326,1413,"Mrs. Grant,"],[1447,1564,"are we sure there hasn't been"],[1564,1639,"some mistake?"],[1789,1864,"Girls like that?"],[1893,1985,"I've seen too many."],[2035,2164,"Selling themselves for money."],[2268,2485,"Whatever happens, they asked for it."],[2502,2531,"Come on,"],[2531,2631,"we're gonna be late for the finals."],[2648,2798,"Sure, it's just,"],[2865,2915,"there was something"],[2915,2977,"about her."],[3028,3136,"The way she looked at you."],[3215,3478,"Her eyes were just as clear as yours."],[3499,3536,"I don't know,"],[3536,3670,"she didn't seem that bad of a girl."],[3878,4008,"Help me, please stop!"],[4058,4149,"Mrs. Grant!"],[4266,4379,"Hand me the competition list."]],"45":[[558,696,"You fucking bitch!"],[742,875,"You think you can hit me and run?"],[967,1117,"I'm gonna teach you a lesson."],[1188,1247,"Strip her."],[1401,1480,"No, please."],[1518,1559,"Please!"],[1693,1805,"Get off, please!"],[1805,1843,"Stop!"],[1843,2018,"Go on, scream louder!"],[2118,2260,"I'm gonna post it online."],[2260,2356,"Let the world see"],[2373,2610,"what kind of slut you really are."],[3194,3353,"You crazy bitch, did you just bite me?"],[3374,3457,"This is assault."],[3457,3582,"I'm calling the cops."],[3645,3762,"Calling the cops?"],[3799,3908,"You wish."],[3966,4008,"Help!"],[4049,4187,"Somebody help me, please!"],[4233,4346,"Don't let her leave."],[4471,4608,"She's all yours."],[4700,4842,"Nobody's gonna come save you,"],[4842,4896,"baby."],[4954,5105,"Let me take real good care of you."],[5192,5230,"No."],[5280,5388,"Get off, please!"],[5651,5855,"Once this video hits the school forum,"],[5855,6010,"that bitch is finished!"],[6076,6114,"Stop!"],[6114,6202,"Get off of her!"]],"46":[[33,79,"Stop!"],[79,175,"Get off of her!"],[254,304,"What the..."],[696,855,"God, I was wrong about her."],[950,1092,"Don't you dare touch her!"],[1493,1572,"Mrs. Grant!"],[1609,1768,"Who the hell is this old hag?"],[1801,1901,"Back up, old lady,"],[1939,2052,"or you're gonna be next."],[2052,2114,"Don't touch her!"],[2444,2481,"Fine."],[2556,2640,"Then you'll take her place."],[2927,3240,"Nobody touches my people."],[3720,3778,"What?"],[3899,3958,"Bitch!"],[4008,4099,"Get out of here."],[4120,4266,"This has nothing to do with you."],[4279,4421,"No, you need to get out of here."],[4487,4567,"Do you even know"],[4583,4704,"who owns this school?"],[4775,4875,"Of course I do."],[4921,5050,"Saint Peter's Academy,"],[5092,5234,"funded by the Grant family,"],[5246,5363,"the most important family"],[5363,5434,"in the country."],[5484,5580,"So what?"],[5626,5689,"So you do know"],[5689,5780,"who owns this place."],[5864,5976,"Then you should know better."],[6006,6235,"My dad is the vice principal."],[6343,6481,"Who do you think you are?"],[6510,6627,"Rachel Grant?"],[6731,6906,"She is Rachel Grant."],[6973,7061,"Yeah, sure."],[7061,7186,"You think I'll believe that?"],[7219,7294,"You wanna help her?"],[7344,7394,"Fine."],[7428,7557,"Then we'll fuck you up too."],[7603,7649,"Tom!"],[7903,7962,"Dolores!"],[7987,8074,"Dolores!"]],"47":[[179,262,"Dolores!"],[475,558,"Oh my god."],[684,796,"Ma'am, are you all right?"],[859,930,"Hold them down."],[955,1005,"Now!"],[1030,1076,"On it."],[1117,1222,"You can't do this!"],[1259,1401,"My dad's the vice principal."],[1418,1522,"If you touch me,"],[1530,1726,"the Grant family will have your heads."],[1755,1843,"Tom, come on!"],[2189,2243,"Idiot."],[2281,2327,"Who do you think"],[2327,2410,"you're messing with?"],[2464,2602,"This is Rachel Grant,"],[2627,2761,"head of the Grant empire."],[2815,2936,"Wait, what?"],[3040,3199,"She's really Rachel Grant?"],[3261,3382,"No one pulls this kind of stunt"],[3382,3499,"on my campus."],[3557,3620,"And you!"],[3728,3937,"How dare you trying to bully"],[3937,4045,"someone like this?"],[4066,4183,"Do you have a death wish?"],[4225,4383,"No, no, no, no, no, it wasn't me."],[4408,4525,"It was Sara."],[4558,4658,"She told me to do it."],[4704,4779,"She knew this girl"],[4779,4917,"was gonna be in the competition"],[4917,5034,"and wanted her gone."],[5088,5221,"I just did what I was told."],[5326,5401,"What did you say?"]],"48":[[0,246,"Mrs., Mrs. Grant, it was all Sara's idea."],[258,321,"We were just,"],[329,408,"we were just following"],[408,500,"what she told us to do."],[529,658,"You idiot!"],[688,750,"How dare you"],[750,896,"bring my daughter into this?"],[1063,1255,"Expel them, wipe their phones,"],[1267,1368,"and bring them to the police."],[1393,1438,"On it."],[1906,1972,"The competition"],[1972,2243,"doesn't start for a few hours, so"],[2327,2460,"let's get you patched up."],[2523,2565,"Okay?"],[2602,2648,"Come on."],[3516,3578,"Does it hurt?"],[3778,3874,"Well, all set."],[3908,4083,"Just let that dry for a few days, okay?"],[4166,4237,"What is it?"],[4433,4504,"It's just,"],[4533,4662,"my mom's never taken care of me"],[4662,4758,"like this before."],[4963,5163,"Thank you for what you did earlier."],[5201,5292,"When you stood up for me."],[5317,5488,"No, I should be thanking you."],[5518,5605,"You saved me."],[5668,5772,"I owe you an apology"],[5839,5922,"for how I treated you"],[5922,6010,"when you first arrived."],[6018,6126,"I was wrong about you."],[6235,6473,"So you know I didn't steal Sara's ring?"],[6556,6627,"I do now."],[6677,6760,"She's my daughter,"],[6769,6981,"and I had to believe her."],[7027,7332,"Dolores, Sara is everything to me."],[7415,7561,"I would do anything to protect her."],[7916,8108,"Hi, could you please run a DNA test"],[8108,8204,"on these two samples?"]],"49":[[0,187,"The Grant family art contest"],[187,354,"is no joke this year."],[379,579,"Totally anonymous, no names,"],[583,696,"just the artwork."],[734,813,"Judges vote,"],[859,934,"and whoever gets picked"],[934,1017,"the most wins."],[1059,1247,"And the winner gets the honor"],[1251,1363,"of being awarded"],[1405,1722,"by the legend, Ms. Rachel Grant."],[1768,1922,"It's a major league event too,"],[1960,2127,"internationally certified."],[2198,2410,"First place is half a million dollar,"],[2435,2577,"and the title of America's"],[2594,2823,"Outstanding New Artist of the Year."],[2898,2944,"Honestly,"],[3023,3244,"being here feels unreal."],[3286,3595,"And I heard that Sara, her daughter,"],[3595,3699,"is competing as well."],[3753,3920,"And her mom's hands, they say,"],[3933,4087,"were kissed by God."],[4099,4220,"So if she inherited"],[4233,4441,"even half of her mother's talent,"],[4491,4558,"it's over."],[4825,5363,"That idiot Luna better have handled it. I hate loose ends."],[6110,6235,"Dolores Cooper?"],[6281,6560,"Why is this country girl everywhere?"],[6915,7015,"This is Sara Grant."],[7065,7203,"I need someone taken care of,"],[7219,7294,"quietly."]],"50":[[0,83,"This is Sara Grant."],[145,291,"I need someone taken care of,"],[296,371,"quietly."],[462,571,"The show's about to start."],[617,754,"Luna's probably already"],[754,888,"crushed that bitch."],[917,992,"Hope you're enjoying"],[992,1159,"my little surprise, Dolores."],[1213,1343,"That's what you get for stealing"],[1343,1480,"Grandpa and Ryan from me."],[1801,1914,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[1968,2202,"Ms. Rachel Grant has arrived."]],"51":[[938,1126,"Mom, there you are."],[1163,1226,"Where were you?"],[1284,1401,"I'm so sorry, sweetheart."],[1451,1547,"I had to handle something."],[1597,1722,"Dolores actually helped me with it,"],[1726,1843,"so I invited her along"],[1843,1931,"to get changed."],[2102,2185,"Welcome, everyone."],[2239,2323,"The competition"],[2323,2498,"officially begins now."],[2523,2681,"Judges, take your time,"],[2719,2844,"review each piece,"],[2844,2940,"and cast your vote."],[2957,3069,"You'll have one hour."],[3094,3290,"To keep it fair, please refrain"],[3290,3470,"from speaking to the contestants."],[3770,3949,"After intense deliberation,"],[3995,4124,"one painting stood out"],[4166,4354,"and received a unanimous vote."],[4371,4441,"That's right,"],[4466,4642,"every single judge chose it."],[4671,4871,"Oh my God, a perfect score?"],[4875,5017,"That's never happened."],[5046,5251,"This got to be a masterpiece."],[5292,5426,"This painting channels"],[5426,5605,"Rachel Grant's signature style,"],[5638,5789,"but adds an emotional depth"],[5789,5993,"that left the judges speechless."],[6014,6252,"Any guesses as to who this artist is?"],[6306,6423,"Something that deep"],[6460,6560,"and in her style,"],[6598,6890,"it got to be Sara Grant, right?"],[6923,7048,"Sara's improved a lot."],[7090,7211,"To paint something this close"],[7211,7290,"to my style,"],[7361,7524,"she must've worked so hard."],[7636,7716,"All right, folks."],[7732,7820,"Moment of truth."],[7857,8028,"Let's unveil the winning piece."],[8074,8179,"And the artist is"],[8229,8387,"Dolores Cooper."]],"52":[[1284,1363,"Hi, everyone."],[1443,1576,"I'm Dolores Cooper."],[1697,1751,"To be honest,"],[1751,1856,"I didn't start painting"],[1856,1964,"because I loved it."],[1997,2152,"I did it because I wanted to be seen"],[2264,2398,"and because I needed money."],[2961,3186,"What a shallow little gold-digger."],[3240,3386,"She is an insult to art."],[3474,3591,"I didn't come from much."],[3636,3728,"My aunt's always loved me"],[3728,3812,"with all of her heart"],[3812,3958,"and my mom,"],[4037,4158,"she's tough,"],[4204,4312,"but she has a good heart."],[4387,4475,"She went through hell"],[4475,4596,"bringing me into this world"],[4596,4679,"and raising me."],[4754,4934,"It hasn't been easy for either of us."],[5000,5100,"So that's why I paint."],[5142,5313,"Maybe one day if I make it big,"],[5376,5526,"she won't suffer anymore."],[5634,5718,"Most people"],[5718,5809,"wouldn't call my mother"],[5809,5914,"a good mother."],[6051,6164,"Get your ass in there!"],[6398,6602,"She's hurt me more than she's cared."]],"53":[[20,108,"Most people"],[112,200,"wouldn't call my mother"],[200,300,"a good mother."],[375,575,"She's hurt me more than she's cared."],[667,859,"She's left scars instead of hugs."],[1005,1359,"But I still believe that deep down,"],[1413,1522,"she really loves me."],[1714,1851,"My Aunt Rose once told me"],[1906,1956,"when my mother"],[1956,2081,"was giving birth to me,"],[2081,2206,"she nearly died."],[2314,2389,"No mother"],[2448,2598,"fights that hard to bring a child"],[2598,2765,"into this world without love."],[2898,2957,"One day,"],[3032,3219,"I wanna melt the ice around her heart"],[3303,3482,"because I'm her daughter"],[3578,3874,"and I love her more than anything."],[3933,4154,"My dream is to give her the life"],[4154,4250,"that she never had."],[4283,4450,"One that's filled with warmth"],[4483,4596,"and joy and"],[4708,4871,"everything that she's ever wanted."],[4921,5025,"And that's why I painted this."],[5171,5230,"Thank you."]],"54":[[1668,1872,"Sweetheart, can I give you a hug?"],[1889,1989,"Of course."],[3148,3265,"Your mom may not show it,"],[3294,3374,"but trust me,"],[3449,3524,"she loves you"],[3599,3670,"more than you know."]],"55":[[387,575,"That girl's really something."],[600,784,"Add another five hundred grand"],[784,938,"to the prize from me."],[955,1088,"Tell her it's a sponsorship."],[1088,1213,"I want her to keep painting."],[1276,1351,"Understood, sir."],[1397,1614,"They look so much alike,"],[1647,1856,"even standing next to each other."],[1906,1989,"About that, sir."],[2097,2173,"When you had me look"],[2173,2289,"into Dolores's background,"],[2289,2431,"I found something strange."],[3032,3219,"What do you mean, strange?"],[3290,3403,"Dolores and Miss Grant"],[3486,3628,"were born at the same hospital"],[3724,3799,"on the same day."],[4145,4183,"What?"],[5663,5743,"Who the hell are you?"]],"56":[[171,266,"Thank you for coming tonight"],[266,367,"to cheer me on, Ryan."],[417,450,"Yeah."],[525,579,"Like I said,"],[613,717,"you're gonna be the brightest star"],[717,763,"out there."],[1634,1826,"Um, I gotta go inside."],[1897,1968,"Oh, wait."],[4137,4300,"Dolores, I wanna be that guy"],[4300,4512,"that stands tall next to you,"],[4583,4700,"the person who protects you."],[4742,4854,"Will you be my girlfriend?"],[5213,5276,"Dolores!"],[5488,5559,"My mom's here."],[5563,5676,"You gotta go, now."],[5689,5714,"Wait."],[5714,5755,"Go!"],[5755,5801,"Call me."],[5801,5834,"Now!"],[5834,5968,"Don't forget to tell me your answer."],[5993,6031,"Go!"],[6623,6752,"Mom, check it out."],[6810,6861,"I won!"],[6944,7082,"Once that prize money comes in,"],[7140,7332,"I can finally get you and Aunt Rose"],[7357,7457,"out of this place."],[7457,7607,"No more skipped meds."],[7741,7891,"You ungrateful little bitch."],[7907,7991,"Why are you stealing"],[7991,8112,"Miss Grant's trophy"],[8145,8258,"and her boyfriend?"]],"57":[[0,200,"Mom, what are you talking about?"],[241,396,"How many times do I have to tell you?"],[487,721,"You were born to be dirt-poor."],[721,813,"You don't get to steal"],[813,892,"from Miss Grant."],[946,1051,"That's the truth, Sara."],[1201,1359,"I switched you and Dolores."],[1564,1680,"You're my real daughter."],[1739,1918,"Get lost."],[1964,2160,"I don't have a lowlife"],[2164,2352,"pizza-slinging mom like you!"],[2385,2423,"No."],[2423,2565,"Baby, what did you just say?"],[2648,2786,"You swapped me and Dolores,"],[2836,3015,"so why'd you leave Grandpa clues"],[3015,3090,"to suspect?"],[3115,3265,"Why aren't you keeping Dolores"],[3265,3324,"in check?"],[3353,3499,"She keeps stealing everything"],[3499,3574,"that is mine!"],[3620,3770,"She's dared take what's yours?"],[3891,3916,"No."],[3941,4020,"Honey, don't worry."],[4087,4187,"I'll teach her a lesson."],[4262,4379,"She'll give you back everything"],[4379,4504,"that belongs to you, I swear."]],"58":[[20,116,"I'll teach her a lesson."],[196,312,"She'll give you back everything"],[312,437,"that belongs to you, I swear."],[487,742,"I didn't steal anything from Sara."],[850,1034,"I earned this by myself."],[1076,1284,"And he's not even her boyfriend."],[1338,1405,"Cut the crap."],[1497,1572,"Trash like you"],[1601,1726,"doesn't deserve any of this."],[1764,1918,"So if you think of me as your mother,"],[1926,2081,"then you will return that trophy"],[2106,2252,"and you will never speak"],[2252,2348,"to that guy again."],[2394,2460,"So that's it?"],[2569,2719,"I finally earn something"],[2719,2802,"for myself,"],[2902,3036,"and you want me to hand it over"],[3115,3207,"to someone else?"],[3240,3382,"Give up my dreams,"],[3465,3553,"my happiness?"],[3603,3691,"Tell me, Mom,"],[3774,3895,"who's your real daughter?"],[4425,4575,"The DNA results are ready."]],"59":[[642,721,"Dolores isn't"],[721,884,"Molly's biological daughter?"],[1130,1180,"I'm sorry,"],[1180,1205,"do you know"],[1205,1292,"if there's been a mistake?"],[1376,1430,"Positive."],[1451,1614,"Our lab's never messed up a test."],[1639,1714,"Not once."],[2114,2152,"Mom,"],[2235,2406,"no matter how hard I try"],[2498,2715,"or how good I am,"],[2740,2840,"you never care."],[2915,2965,"Why?"],[3040,3178,"Am I not your daughter?"],[3436,3570,"Can't you just love me"],[3595,3778,"just even a little bit?"],[3791,3874,"Stop whining."],[3962,4074,"I don't give a shit!"],[4133,4204,"I told you,"],[4254,4358,"return the trophy"],[4425,4567,"or don't bother coming back!"],[4633,4725,"No matter what I do,"],[4838,4971,"I'll never be good enough for you."],[5034,5071,"Fine."],[5176,5238,"I'm done."],[5330,5472,"I'm done with this house"],[5547,5697,"and with you."]],"60":[[500,600,"I knew that little brat"],[600,754,"didn't have the guts to defy me."],[1209,1267,"Molly!"],[1380,1580,"Your daughter is so amazing."],[1614,1726,"That speech she gave earlier"],[1726,1885,"had me bawling like a baby."],[1922,2043,"We made this pie just for her."],[2227,2285,"Keep it."],[2293,2369,"She doesn't deserve"],[2369,2464,"anything that nice."],[2485,2598,"What speech are you talking about?"],[2677,2777,"Wait, you haven't seen it?"],[2940,3057,"And the artist is"],[3123,3261,"Dolores Cooper!"],[3791,3903,"I didn't come from much."],[3970,4070,"My aunt's always loved me"],[4070,4158,"with all of her heart"],[4158,4283,"and my mom,"],[4366,4466,"she's tough,"],[4466,4642,"but she has a good heart."],[4683,4963,"It hasn't been easy for either of us."],[5096,5326,"My dream is to give her the life"],[5326,5426,"that she never had."],[5501,5780,"One filled with warmth and joy"],[5860,6043,"and everything that she deserves."],[6243,6360,"And that's why I painted this."],[6452,6506,"Thank you."]],"61":[[8,137,"She's a good kid, Molly."],[342,429,"Is she not home?"],[604,725,"It's about to pour out there."],[763,846,"You should go look for her."],[846,875,"What?"],[875,946,"It's already dark."],[946,1080,"What, what if something happens?"],[2147,2281,"Whatever you think of my mother,"],[2281,2423,"it's not your place to judge her."],[2439,2585,"She brought me into this world"],[2585,2715,"and raised me all on her own."],[2736,2923,"To me, she's the strongest,"],[2940,3119,"most incredible woman I know."],[3386,3470,"No, Mom!"],[3470,3549,"Take it off!"],[3570,3649,"I'm your daughter!"],[3649,3753,"Why are you doing this to me?"],[3962,4116,"Dolores, why?"],[4133,4300,"Why are you still so nice to me"],[4308,4462,"after everything I've done?"]],"62":[[663,779,"Why did you ask me to come up here?"],[896,975,"My mom told me"],[1076,1159,"to give this to you."],[1505,1664,"You think I want your pity?"],[1805,1885,"My whole life,"],[1985,2210,"no one has dared to take what's mine."],[2227,2285,"But you?"],[2402,2469,"You're the first."],[2535,2648,"Ever since you showed up,"],[2686,2882,"everything has gone to hell."],[2911,3044,"You took my grandpa's attention,"],[3098,3186,"my mom's approval,"],[3203,3340,"even Ryan, and now,"],[3415,3478,"my trophy."],[3507,3603,"And you walk in"],[3603,3807,"like some sad, pitiful little orphan,"],[3816,3895,"and suddenly,"],[3916,4120,"nobody sees me anymore."],[4208,4400,"So let me get one thing clear."],[4479,4671,"Nobody takes what's mine."],[4758,4829,"Dolores!"],[4879,4959,"Not my life."],[5009,5109,"Not my place."],[5146,5280,"And not you!"],[5305,5422,"So go to hell!"],[5955,6022,"Dolores!"],[6035,6097,"Sara!"]],"63":[[567,617,"Hang on!"],[617,658,"Hang on!"],[658,746,"Mommy's got you!"],[767,838,"Mommy's got you!"],[838,892,"Don't be scared."],[917,980,"Don't be scared."],[1001,1188,"Help me, please!"],[1188,1330,"I don't want to die!"],[1330,1413,"Pull me up!"],[1426,1505,"Please!"],[1568,1630,"Let go"],[1630,1743,"or you'll fall too!"],[1968,2118,"You can only save one of us!"],[2143,2243,"You pick me!"],[2256,2335,"Choose me!"],[2373,2423,"My girl."],[2502,2640,"Sara's my real daughter."],[2665,2823,"She has her whole life ahead of her."],[2823,2961,"I can't lose her, I can't!"],[3966,4045,"I'm sorry."],[5201,5242,"Mom,"],[5317,5401,"you abandoned me."],[5518,5563,"Again."]],"64":[[137,208,"Dolores!"],[804,909,"I'm right here, sweetie."],[934,980,"Hold on!"],[988,1059,"Can you hear me?"],[1288,1476,"Aunt, Aunt Rose."],[1493,1564,"Hold on!"],[3015,3086,"How's Dolores?"],[3086,3157,"Is she okay?"],[3332,3511,"You heartless monster."],[3541,3645,"You let her fall."],[3645,3799,"You let her fall to her death!"],[3828,3924,"What are you talking about?"],[3924,4012,"She's my daughter."],[4012,4158,"I didn't want this to happen."],[4208,4362,"But she just ran off by herself,"],[4362,4462,"so what was I supposed to do?"],[4462,4517,"Enough!"],[4617,4829,"Is Dolores really your daughter?"]],"65":[[25,83,"What do you mean?"],[150,258,"It's always baffled me."],[337,475,"Dolores is the kindest,"],[492,667,"most thoughtful kid I've ever met."],[667,729,"And you!"],[792,880,"You beat her."],[930,1051,"You humiliated her."],[1051,1205,"You crushed her dreams."],[1272,1397,"You told her she couldn't paint,"],[1397,1480,"couldn't go to school."],[1480,1685,"What kind of mother does that?"],[1714,1864,"I was just trying to get her"],[1864,1981,"to accept reality."],[1981,2077,"Whose reality?"],[2081,2360,"She was born to rot in the slums!"],[2360,2535,"That is the life that was meant for her!"],[2552,2794,"No, that's the life you forced on her,"],[2869,3028,"not the one she deserves."],[3103,3290,"Because she's not your daughter."],[3457,3507,"Shut up."],[3582,3674,"Do you hear yourself?"],[3720,3757,"Here."],[3787,3883,"Read this."],[4717,4800,"I've always wondered"],[4829,5013,"why you treat Dolores like trash,"],[5013,5142,"but bent over backwards"],[5142,5246,"for the Grand's daughter."],[5276,5442,"Even tonight, you let her fall"],[5442,5568,"just to save that girl."],[5626,5726,"Now I get it."],[5747,5968,"You took your ugly duckling"],[6006,6202,"and turned her into a swan,"],[6256,6381,"leaving the real princess"],[6381,6489,"to rot in the dirt"],[6489,6594,"like she was nothing."],[6706,6856,"You swapped them!"]],"66":[[112,296,"Sir, my daughter Sara, is she alright?"],[304,446,"She's fine."],[496,613,"Just some minor scrapes,"],[646,767,"no internal injuries."],[779,871,"She's still shaken up,"],[892,1059,"but physically she'll be fine."],[1172,1238,"Mom!"],[1305,1393,"Oh my God."],[1476,1526,"Sweetie!"],[1564,1643,"What happened?"],[1705,1793,"How did you fall?"],[1851,1939,"She pushed me."],[1989,2031,"What?"],[2281,2423,"And I actually stood up for her."],[2464,2585,"And she tried to hurt my daughter?"],[2669,2752,"Don't worry, baby."],[2794,2911,"She will not get away with this."],[3207,3282,"Call the legal team."],[3311,3365,"The best lawyers"],[3365,3457,"the Grand family has."],[3503,3649,"I don't care what it costs."],[3649,3895,"She's going to prison for life."],[4041,4183,"Dolores, I'll make sure your"],[4183,4763,"real mother sends you straight to hell."],[5046,5138,"Doctor, how is she?"],[5163,5230,"How's Dolores?"],[5259,5347,"She's stable."],[5376,5467,"We were able to treat"],[5467,5609,"her external injuries,"],[5680,5809,"but during examination,"],[5809,5960,"we found something more serious."],[6156,6377,"Dolores has aplastic leukemia,"],[6398,6589,"which is rare and life-threatening."],[6610,6690,"She needs treatment"],[6690,6777,"right away or"],[6819,6894,"she might not make it."]],"67":[[133,271,"Aplastic leukemia?"],[379,496,"No, no, no!"],[496,700,"Doctor, please, you have to save her."],[700,788,"She's just a kid."],[788,942,"She has her whole life ahead of her."],[967,1067,"The only option now"],[1067,1217,"is to do a bone marrow transplant."],[1234,1309,"And to do that"],[1309,1501,"we need a direct blood relative."],[1530,1572,"One of you"],[1572,1685,"should get tested right away."],[1789,1906,"A direct relative?"],[2181,2289,"I know who we can ask."],[2406,2439,"No!"],[2473,2577,"No, no, no!"],[2577,2669,"No, you can't!"],[2669,2815,"Seriously, Molly? - No!"],[2827,3011,"You're still trying to cover this up?"],[3065,3207,"Dolores is dying!"],[3265,3353,"Please."],[3411,3549,"If you tell the truth now"],[3549,3753,"it's going to ruin Sara's life."],[3799,3912,"Everything that she has,"],[3912,4012,"everything that we built,"],[4041,4120,"it'll all be gone."],[4204,4266,"No, please."],[4279,4375,"There has to be another way"],[4375,4433,"to save Dolores!"],[4433,4550,"Get out of my way!"]],"68":[[29,141,"Just take care of her, Doctor."],[141,221,"Whatever it takes."],[225,392,"My daughter deserves the best."],[400,483,"No matter the cost."],[742,796,"Rachel!"],[925,1055,"Please, come with me."],[1088,1180,"Dolores needs you."],[1205,1426,"Get your filthy hands off of me!"],[1584,1626,"No!"],[1668,1705,"No!"],[1705,1822,"Dolores has leukemia!"],[1868,1943,"She's dying!"],[2002,2068,"The doctors say"],[2093,2181,"you're the only match."],[2181,2348,"You're the only one who can save her."],[2494,2610,"She nearly killed my daughter."],[2615,2769,"Why the hell would I want to save her?"],[2944,3111,"No, this is karma."],[3186,3319,"She could rot in that hospital bed"],[3319,3395,"for all I care."],[3478,3545,"You know what?"],[3607,3707,"She can die there."],[3770,3949,"She's your real daughter, Rachel!"]],"69":[[20,162,"Sara's not your daughter."],[271,479,"Dolores is your real"],[483,633,"biological daughter."],[763,875,"What the hell is going on?"],[875,1026,"I mean, that's impossible!"],[1034,1138,"Mom, she's lying!"],[1138,1242,"She's crazy!"],[1247,1401,"Don't listen to anything she says!"],[1443,1601,"Dolores was never my niece."],[1626,1751,"How on earth did I end up"],[1751,1956,"with Sara as my niece instead?"],[1985,2168,"Mom, please just get this lunatic"],[2168,2252,"out of here!"],[2344,2389,"Wait."],[2548,2623,"Let her finish."],[2706,2819,"Check Sara's palm."],[2944,3044,"She has a red birthmark,"],[3044,3103,"doesn't she?"],[3148,3311,"That mark runs in my family."],[3386,3503,"Sixteen years ago,"],[3561,3724,"you and my sister gave birth"],[3724,3866,"in the same hospital."],[3970,4149,"She switched the babies."],[4204,4304,"She raised yours,"],[4371,4504,"and you raised hers."],[5910,5955,"Yeah?"],[6026,6206,"Sir, the DNA results between"],[6206,6456,"Mrs. Grant and Dolores are in."]],"70":[[58,116,"Mom!"],[141,216,"She's lying!"],[216,383,"That is Dolores' aunt!"],[400,487,"She just wants to help her"],[487,629,"take everything from me!"],[629,696,"Bullshit!"],[946,1080,"I won't press charges for the fall."],[1088,1309,"Just please don't let her"],[1309,1413,"anywhere near me again."],[1605,1680,"This is pathetic."],[1726,1822,"You people really think"],[1822,1939,"I'm gonna take the side"],[1939,2052,"of some lowlife girl"],[2052,2177,"over my own daughter?"],[2298,2506,"Tell Dolores to lawyer up."],[2531,2631,"She's going to regret"],[2660,2840,"ever stepping foot into our lives."],[3136,3190,"Please."],[3290,3486,"Dolores is your daughter,"],[3524,3607,"and she's dying."],[3653,3820,"You're the only one who can save her."],[3883,3937,"Please,"],[3945,4062,"do whatever you want to me."],[4066,4233,"Just save her."],[4446,4500,"Mom."]],"71":[[120,225,"I don't know what makes you so sure"],[225,371,"that I'm the one that can save Dolores."],[421,538,"Even if she were innocent,"],[583,738,"she tried to hurt my daughter."],[771,946,"There is no way in hell"],[946,1142,"I'm lifting a finger to help her out."],[1172,1259,"Take her away."],[1267,1393,"Let the cops sort her out."],[1422,1459,"No!"],[1501,1651,"No, you're making a huge mistake!"],[1693,1797,"You'll regret this!"],[1860,1906,"No!"],[1939,1972,"No!"],[2035,2089,"Please!"],[2844,2919,"Oh, you're awake!"],[2919,2977,"Thank God."],[3069,3182,"What happened?"],[3215,3340,"You fell from a rooftop."],[3415,3457,"Luckily,"],[3457,3632,"some tree branches broke your fall."],[3682,3824,"Just a few cuts and bruises."],[4204,4279,"I'm sorry."],[4683,4808,"There's something else."],[4850,5005,"Your family didn't want us to tell you,"],[5005,5267,"but you deserve to know."],[5855,6026,"Aplastic leukemia?"]],"72":[[471,533,"You're awake."],[704,813,"It's Christmas."],[925,1021,"It's my birthday."],[1088,1155,"Do you remember?"],[1372,1413,"So?"],[1534,1597,"You don't expect me"],[1597,1714,"to throw you a party, do you?"],[1801,1901,"I don't have time for that."],[1901,2043,"No, that's not what I meant."],[2156,2252,"I was just thinking,"],[2327,2494,"you gave birth to me on Christmas"],[2494,2615,"and after all these years,"],[2615,2727,"I don't think I've ever given you"],[2727,2806,"anything back."],[3536,3611,"This is for you."],[3699,3766,"This is all the money"],[3766,3828,"I've saved up"],[3828,3999,"every Christmas since I was little."],[4287,4408,"I'm skipping treatment."],[4596,4821,"Just take it and use it, please."]],"73":[[358,492,"I hope Mom's happy every day."],[513,633,"I hope Mom never gets sick."],[633,742,"I hope I grow up fast"],[742,817,"so Mom doesn't have to"],[817,859,"work so hard."],[859,1038,"I hope Mom loves me a little more."],[1463,1647,"Aunt Rose said if I wrote my wishes"],[1647,1768,"and put them in the piggy bank"],[1835,1918,"at Christmas,"],[2018,2131,"Santa would make my dreams"],[2131,2193,"come true."],[2323,2410,"After I'm gone,"],[2469,2515,"there's no one"],[2515,2652,"that will be able to take care of you."],[2836,2969,"I hope this helps, Mom."],[4195,4325,"Dolores, you're not mad at me?"],[4600,4679,"I'm your daughter."],[4833,4954,"How could I be mad at you?"],[5025,5146,"I just want you to be happy."],[5701,5780,"I'm sorry."],[5780,5893,"I'm so sorry."]],"74":[[617,696,"I don't want your money."],[738,821,"You need to worry about"],[821,905,"saving yourself."],[959,1051,"Don't try to save me."],[1109,1234,"I'm going to make Rachel save you."],[1355,1405,"Mom!"],[1418,1463,"Mom!"],[2252,2344,"Please leave your message"],[2344,2427,"after the tone."],[2460,2623,"Since I confessed to Dolores that day,"],[2665,2786,"I haven't heard a word from her."],[2915,3011,"Did I scare her off?"],[3228,3299,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[3299,3445,"thank you for joining me tonight"],[3445,3620,"to celebrate my daughter's birthday."],[3632,3845,"God gave me to her on Christmas,"],[3908,4029,"my greatest gift."],[4133,4325,"So tonight I have one more"],[4325,4441,"announcement to make."]],"75":[[70,304,"I'll be transferring all of my shares"],[325,412,"to Sara."],[454,496,"Yes."],[529,709,"From today moving forward,"],[709,859,"she will be the rightful heir"],[859,1076,"of the Grant family legacy."],[1151,1259,"Mom, thank you!"],[1755,1810,"Rachel,"],[1951,2077,"you have to save Dolores."],[2173,2260,"Who let her in here?"],[2273,2306,"Rachel,"],[2306,2444,"there's something you have to know."],[2481,2577,"No, no."],[2585,2644,"Don't hurt her!"],[2669,2802,"Throw them out!"],[2811,2940,"Mom, are you okay?"],[3478,3641,"You have to save Dolores."],[3799,3999,"Because Dolores is your real daughter."]],"76":[[137,337,"Because Dolores is your real daughter."],[1142,1205,"You're lying."],[1230,1322,"No, I'm not."],[1397,1484,"I came here tonight"],[1484,1651,"to finally tell you the truth."],[1993,2047,"Shut up!"],[2235,2327,"Mom, don't believe them."],[2369,2540,"They're just poor corn artists"],[2540,2598,"trying to ruin me,"],[2598,2702,"just like her aunt did."],[2752,2827,"Don't worry, sweetie."],[2848,3015,"I wouldn't believe two sewer rats."],[3165,3282,"First you hurt my daughter,"],[3324,3390,"and now you"],[3390,3570,"and your pathetic excuse of a mother"],[3570,3707,"are trying to steal her life?"],[3732,3874,"No, I would never-"],[3874,3937,"Enough!"],[3999,4116,"I don't care if you drop dead"],[4116,4283,"now or tomorrow."],[4312,4450,"Take your trashy mother"],[4450,4633,"and get the hell out of here."],[4667,4717,"Okay."],[4721,4808,"Fine, Mom."],[4867,4946,"Let's just go."],[5034,5071,"No!"]],"77":[[54,258,"Rachel, Dolores is your real daughter."],[458,529,"Give it to me."],[638,796,"That is the necklace you gave Dolores!"],[796,875,"It's proof!"],[1234,1284,"Watch out!"],[1705,1893,"That's enough!"],[2152,2335,"Dolores is your daughter."]],"78":[[692,792,"Take a look at this."],[1205,1297,"You won."],[1430,1601,"Dolores is my real daughter?"],[1701,1822,"What the hell is going on?"],[3244,3349,"Sixteen years ago"],[3349,3507,"I did something unforgivable."],[3591,3774,"I switched our babies, Rachel."]],"79":[[62,129,"I wanted,"],[162,316,"I wanted to punish Colton"],[333,429,"for abandoning me,"],[521,754,"so I made your daughter"],[909,1038,"live the life of a nobody"],[1092,1242,"while mine got to be the princess"],[1242,1343,"of the Grant family."],[1468,1559,"But that necklace,"],[1626,1839,"Dolores kept it all this time."],[1889,2022,"She thought it was from me."],[2189,2293,"But it was really from you."],[2439,2569,"You monster!"],[2652,2702,"How could you"],[2702,2819,"involve innocent children"],[2819,2944,"into your petty revenge?"],[2957,3111,"You nearly ruined my daughter's life!"],[3286,3453,"I regret it."],[3453,3586,"I regret everything."],[3699,3874,"Dolores is so kind."],[3912,4037,"No matter how horrible"],[4049,4129,"I treated her,"],[4133,4266,"she always loved me."],[4325,4441,"I'm so sorry."],[4458,4575,"This is all my fault."],[4575,4662,"I'm so sorry."],[4696,4763,"I..."],[4775,4917,"But, Rachel, you're her Mom,"],[4917,4963,"you can,"],[4979,5088,"you can save her."]],"80":[[0,145,"Mom, please don't leave me."],[150,296,"Mom, I'm your daughter too."],[296,525,"You raised me for sixteen years."],[692,896,"Have a look at this before you decide."],[1026,1142,"So go to hell!"],[1434,1718,"Our little angel isn't so innocent."],[1793,1939,"You nearly killed Dolores."],[1976,2081,"I almost helped you"],[2081,2185,"kill my real daughter."],[2185,2335,"No, Mom, it's not what you think!"],[2339,2385,"Mom!"],[2594,2648,"Take her away."],[2706,2777,"Throw her in jail."],[2827,2886,"And while you're at it,"],[2886,3057,"put my fucking cheating husband"],[3057,3115,"in there too."],[3132,3199,"I don't ever want to see"],[3199,3382,"either of them ever again."],[3407,3520,"No, Mom, please!"],[3520,3661,"No, you can't do this!"],[3687,3828,"Please, I'm sorry, Mom!"],[3828,3920,"No, Mom!"],[3920,3962,"No!"],[4045,4095,"No!"],[4162,4195,"No!"],[4200,4241,"No!"],[4517,4596,"Dolores,"],[4671,4783,"I'm so sorry."],[4863,4975,"I failed you."],[5259,5296,"No."],[5434,5472,"No."],[5505,5538,"No, no, no."],[5538,5605,"This can't be true!"],[5605,5663,"Stay back!"],[5701,5843,"All of you, just stay back!"],[5855,5889,"No!"],[5955,6039,"Dolores!"],[6081,6168,"Dolores!"]],"81":[[984,1138,"Jingle bells."],[1247,1526,"Jingle all the way."],[2623,2711,"Dolores, please!"],[2723,2815,"It's dangerous."],[2823,2911,"Dolores, please."],[2911,3007,"Get down from there."],[3007,3107,"It's dangerous."],[3148,3207,"Stay back."],[3236,3336,"Don't come any closer."],[3436,3549,"Oh, oh, okay, okay, okay."],[3570,3732,"We're staying right here."],[3803,3924,"Dolores, sweetheart,"],[4020,4141,"please just calm down."]],"82":[[150,233,"All this time,"],[421,475,"I thought,"],[575,721,"I thought my mother really loved me."],[763,884,"I thought that she just doesn't know"],[884,963,"how to show it."],[1038,1155,"So I tried to be better,"],[1238,1463,"more obedient, more accomplished."],[1488,1672,"Just maybe so one day"],[1735,1851,"she could love me back."],[2022,2147,"But it turns out that"],[2156,2314,"I'm not even her daughter at all."],[2552,2615,"And that the woman"],[2615,2769,"who treated me like garbage,"],[2886,3065,"she's the one who gave birth to me."],[3294,3490,"No, no, baby, it's not like that."],[3495,3616,"I'm sorry, sweetheart."],[3670,3782,"Please don't do this."],[3853,3949,"Because if you die,"],[4041,4129,"I die too."],[4200,4262,"Dolores,"],[4346,4408,"look at me."],[4471,4537,"I love you."],[4617,4825,"Please, don't leave me like this."],[4909,5009,"I'm sorry, Ryan."],[5167,5305,"I'm just so tired."],[5772,5843,"No!"]],"83":[[191,279,"Dolores!"],[462,525,"Hold on!"],[525,684,"Hold on to Mommy!"],[750,813,"Don't let go!"],[1121,1317,"This time, Mom,"],[1317,1476,"I'm the one letting go."],[1589,1634,"No!"],[1960,2014,"No!"],[4058,4191,"Why is she still unconscious?"],[4220,4304,"We already gave her"],[4304,4416,"the bone marrow transplant."],[4471,4629,"The doctor said that she's refusing"],[4629,4696,"to wake up."],[4733,4921,"Deep down, she's rejecting all of us."],[4954,5063,"It's all my fault."],[5100,5251,"I'm so sorry, sweetheart."],[5276,5359,"Mommy was wrong."],[5476,5568,"And I've punished everyone"],[5568,5668,"that's ever hurt you."],[5772,5868,"Please open your eyes."],[6010,6076,"Mommy wants to spend"],[6076,6168,"your birthday with you."],[6231,6293,"Dolores,"],[6473,6577,"do you remember what I told you?"],[6639,6756,"Your life is yours."],[6986,7119,"Please, you don't have to suffer"],[7119,7236,"for what other people did."],[7298,7369,"You don't have to hide"],[7369,7436,"in the darkness."],[7436,7553,"You deserve to be in the light."],[8145,8291,"Please come back to me, Princess."]]}